          <div class='pagegroup'><a href='http://sli.ics.uci.edu/PmWiki'>PmWiki</a> /</div>
          <h1 class='pagetitle'>WikiStyles</h1></div>
<!--PageText-->
<div id='wikitext'>
<p>
<a name='trailstart' id='trailstart'></a> 
</p><div style='clear:right; float:right; font-size:smaller; background-color:#eee;' >
<p><span class='wikitrail'>&lt; <a class='wikilink' href='http://sli.ics.uci.edu/PmWiki/TableDirectives'>Table directives</a> | <a class='wikilink' href='http://sli.ics.uci.edu/PmWiki/DocumentationIndex#trailstart'>Documentation Index</a> | <a class='wikilink' href='http://sli.ics.uci.edu/PmWiki/WikiStyleExamples'>Wiki style examples</a> &gt;</span> 
</p></div>
<div style='clear:right;' ><span class='frame rfloat' style='font-size: smaller; background-color: #ffffcc; clear: right;'>authors (basic, advanced) </span>
</div>
<div class='rfloat frame' style='clear:right; font-size:small;' >
<p><strong>Contents</strong>
</p><ul><li><a href='#Basics'>Basics</a>
</li><li><a href='#Scope'>Scope</a>
</li><li><a href='#blocks'>In tables and directives</a>
</li><li><a href='#Attributes'>Attributes</a>
</li><li><a href='#Styles'>Enabling Styles</a>
</li><li><a href='#Shortcuts'>Custom style shortcuts</a>
</li><li><a href='#predefined'>Predefined Style Shortcuts</a>
